description: Returns the list of event trackers associated with the account. The response provides the properties for each event tracker, including the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) and tracking ID. For more information on event trackers, see CreateEventTracker.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the event tracker.

nested_items.name: eventTrackerArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the event tracker.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the event tracker.
CREATE PENDING > CREATE IN_PROGRESS > ACTIVE -or- CREATE FAILED.

nested_items.name: creationDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time (in Unix time) that the event tracker was created.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time (in Unix time) that the event tracker was last updated.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token for getting the next set of event trackers (if they exist).
